            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大  一周計累跌1%至2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後升幅擴大，惟一周計累跌，深股跌逾2%，兩市合計成交22001.49億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日收報4124點，升15點或0.25%，早段低見4085點，跌23點或0.56%，為全日低位，即拾級而上，午後升破上午高位，見4129點，升21點或0.51%，全日成交9788.06億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一周累跌38點或0.93%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指全日升83點或0.59%，報14172點，早段見13969，跌119點或0.84%，為全日低位，隨即一直向上，轉跌為升，午後升破上午高位，最高見14212，升124點或0.88%，全日成交12213.43億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一周計跌323點或2.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300收升12點或0.37%，報4660點 ; 創業板指數升12點或0.38%，報3229點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15713866-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e7%b4%af%e8%b7%8c1%e8%87%b32",
