        {
            "title": "A股跌轉升  近半日高位收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日轉升，以接近半日高位收市，兩市合計成交13852.82億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日收報4118點，升10點或0.25%，早段低見4085點，跌23點或0.56%，為半日低位，即拾級而上，最高見4119，升11點或0.27%，半日成交6099.23億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日升112點或0.8%，報14201點，早段見13969，跌119點或0.84%，隨即一直向上，轉跌為升，最高見14202，升113點或0.8%，半日成交7753.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300收升9點或0.2%，報4656點 ; 創業板指數升27點或0.85%，報3244點。</p>\n</div>",
